headline: Waste Management (NYSE:WM) Expands with Stericycle Integration, Eyes Renewable Energy Growth
summary: Waste Management has recently showcased strong operational performance, achieving double-digit growth in operating EBITDA and a notable margin of 30.5%, driven by effective cost optimization and disciplined pricing. The company's focus on sustainability is evident with the completion of 24 out of 39 planned recycling projects, enhancing capacity and efficiency, while strategic acquisitions like Stericycle are set to broaden its market reach.
